OL,3,CRetired Army colonel 'died after four-
OL,4,Chour ambulance delay outside hospital'
OL,6,FA former senior Army officer died
OL,7,Fafter waiting more than four hours in
OL,8,Fthe back of an ambulance stuck outside
OL,9,Fa busy hospital because there was no
OL,10,Fbed for him, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FColonel John Codd, 88, died in Royal
OL,13,FCornwall Hospital in Truro on January
OL,14,F16 this year after suffering a fall
OL,15,Fearlier that day.
OL,17,FMr Codd, who was known as Bill, had
OL,18,Ffallen as he got out a taxi which was
OL,19,Freturning him to a nursing home in St
OL,20,FAustell where he was receiving respite
OL,21,Fcare.
