OL,3,CRetired Army colonel 'died after four-
OL,4,Chour ambulance delay outside hospital'
OL,6,FCornwall Coroner's Court heard Col
OL,7,FCodd, from St Austell, had fallen onto
OL,8,Fthe ground outside the home at 12.30pm
OL,9,Fand staff called for an ambulance.
OL,11,FThe ambulance reached Col Codd at
OL,12,F2.49pm ` two hours and 14 minutes
OL,13,Fafter first being categorised as
OL,14,Fneeding a response within an hour ` as
OL,15,Fhe lay on the ground covered in
OL,16,Fblankets.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
