OL,3,CRetired Army colonel 'died after four-
OL,4,Chour ambulance delay outside hospital'
OL,6,FHe had pre-existing atrial
OL,7,Ffibrillation ` an irregular heartbeat
OL,8,F` and changes in his blood pressure
OL,9,Fnoted during medical reviews by
OL,10,Fdoctors in the emergency department
OL,11,Fwere attributed to this rather than
OL,12,Fthe hematoma.
OL,14,FA report into Col Codd's death by the
OL,15,FSouth West Ambulance Service NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust said delays in
OL,17,Freaching him were due to the hold-ups
OL,18,Fin handing over patients at hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
