OL,3,CRetired Army colonel 'died after four-
OL,4,Chour ambulance delay outside hospital'
OL,6,FEmergency department consultant Dr
OL,7,FAaron Green said those delays were an
OL,8,Fongoing problem.
OL,10,F"It has been an ongoing problem in
OL,11,Fmany departments across the country,
OL,12,Fparticularly in Cornwall, for many
OL,13,Fyears," he told the inquest.
OL,15,FThe inquest heard that for the six
OL,16,Fmonths to January, delays in admitting
OL,17,Fpatients to a ward or sending them
OL,18,Fhome totalled 24,000 hours at the
OL,19,Fhospital ` the equivalent of shutting
OL,20,F32 emergency department cubicles for a
OL,21,Fwhole month.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@GO]
