OL,3,CRetired Army colonel 'died after four-
OL,4,Chour ambulance delay outside hospital'
OL,6,FAndrew Cox, the senior Cornwall
OL,7,FCoroner, said he had previously raised
OL,8,Fconcerns with the hospital and
OL,9,Fambulance trusts about handover delays.
OL,11,F"The problem is the ambulances in the
OL,12,Fwrong place at the wrong time ` they
OL,13,Fare parked outside the emergency
OL,14,Fdepartment at Truro who can't then
OL,15,Frespond to a call," he said.
OL,17,FThe coroner said there were also
OL,18,Fdelays in discharging patients back
OL,19,Finto the community due to a lack of
OL,20,Fsocial care or beds in community
OL,21,Fhospitals.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@SO]
