OL,3,CRetired Army colonel 'died after four-
OL,4,Chour ambulance delay outside hospital'
OL,6,F"This is why I wrote to the Secretary
OL,7,Fof State for Health saying this was a
OL,8,Fsystemic issue. It is not a problem
OL,9,Fthat lies at the door of the South
OL,10,FWest Ambulance Trust or the Royal
OL,11,FCornwall NHS Trust. It is across the
OL,12,Fsystem," he said.
OL,14,F"Unless we get the flow of patients
OL,15,Fthrough the hospital, it bottlenecks
OL,16,Fin the emergency department."
OL,18,FAsked for his view of this, Dr Green
OL,19,Freplied: "I would agree
OL,20,Fwholeheartedly."
