OL,6,FDr Green said if the system had been
OL,7,Fworking properly then Col Codd would
OL,8,Fhave been seen by a doctor within an
OL,9,Fhour and the CT scan would have likely
OL,10,Fbeen ordered earlier.
OL,12,F"That may well have shown evidence of
OL,13,Fthe hematoma. I can't say with
OL,14,Fcertainty that it would have done
OL,15,Fbecause it was something developing
OL,16,Fover time," he said.
OL,18,F"That may have given us time to take a
OL,19,Fdifferent course of action and
OL,20,Fintervene."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@KO]zD@AOU|D@KO]
