OL,6,FThe coroner recorded a narrative
OL,7,Fconclusion and said he would be
OL,8,Fwriting to the Health Secretary to
OL,9,Fraise his concerns about delays in the
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,F"There was a delay in the arrival of
OL,13,Fan ambulance and a further delay in
OL,14,Fhis subsequent admission into
OL,15,Fhospital," he said.
OL,17,F"It is probable that an earlier
OL,18,Fadmission into hospital would have
OL,19,Fresulted in an earlier CT scan being
OL,20,Fperformed that would have revealed the
OL,21,Fpresence of the hematoma.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@JO]yD@AOU
